      <title>拉马福萨签署法律允许储蓄者获取退休基金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/ramaphosa-signs-law-allowing-savers-access-to-retirement-funds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非总统西里尔·拉马福萨签署了一项法律，允许储蓄者提前获得部分退休金。]]></description>
